General utility package for Wikidata Toolkit.

  • Interface Summary

    DirectoryManager
    Interface for classes that read and write files from one directory.
    WebResourceFetcher
    Interface to access files on the Web.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description

    Static helper class for creating DirectoryManager objects.
    DirectoryManagerImpl
    Class to read and write files from one directory.

Package org.wikidata.wdtk.util Description

General utility package for Wikidata Toolkit. Utilities include classes that are so generic that they do not belong into any particular package, and that do not justify an own package either.
Author:
Markus Kroetzsch
